251
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:50,600
I can't accept your feelings, Yun.

252
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:53,350
Whenever you see me, you will think of your brother,

253
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:56,660
and whenever I see you, I will be reminded of Kim Ian, your dead brother.

254
00:25:56,660 --> 00:25:59,570
Is it your dream to continue to play in the Sinyeong Philharmonic?

255
00:25:59,570 --> 00:26:03,460
Not now. I want a new conductor.

256
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:08,190
Do you remember this knife?  Did you kill Ian?

257
00:26:08,190 --> 00:26:09,620
Just a moment.

258
00:26:09,620 --> 00:26:12,380
Wait a moment, Conductor.  I'm almost done.

259
00:26:12,380 --> 00:26:14,610
Excuse me. Who's there?

260
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:17,900
We meet again, Hong Yi Yeong. It's been a long time.
